        <p style="color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <strong>
          \xe2\x80\x9cWe have a cure for cancer. It\xe2\x80\x99s early detection.\xe2\x80\x9d
         </strong>
         <span>
         </span>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <span>
          If you spend any time with
         </span>
         <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/57da5511-4022-4cf6-bea3-deebeba792d7?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">
          Emi Gal
         </a>
         <span>
          , the founder of cancer screening startup
         </span>
         <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/7e877010-29c4-4b9c-957b-382aabb85a07?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">
          Ezra
         </a>
         <span>
          , you\xe2\x80\x99ll hear those two sentences.
         </span>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <span>
          They\xe2\x80\x99re the basis of the company\xe2\x80\x99s mission \xe2\x80\x93
         </span>
         <strong>
          to detect cancer early for everyone in the world
         </strong>
         <span>
          \xe2\x80\x93 one that\xe2\x80\x99s personal for Emi: he\xe2\x80\x99s at high-risk for skin cancer, and sadly lost his mother to metastatic colon cancer after she discovered it too late.
         </span>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         The numbers that back the words up adorn the company\xe2\x80\x99s home page:
        </p>
        <div class="captioned-image-container-static" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 32px auto;">
         <figure style="margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="image-wrapper" data-component-name="Image2ToDOMStatic" style="mso-padding-alt: 1em 0 1.6em;" width="100%">
