          <span>
           Thanks to
          </span>
          <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/4d7db2bc-2daa-4862-aa13-bef668c4855c?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">
